hadiths[13]{hadithnumber,text}:
6940,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz mein dua kartey they ke aey Allah ayaash-bin-abii-rabee'a, Salma bin Hisham aur Waleed bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko nijat de. aey Allah be-bas musalmanon ko nijat de. aey Allah qabila Muzar ke logon ko sakhti ke sath pees daal aur un par aisi qahat saalii bhej jaisi Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamane mein aai thi."
6941,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''teen khususiyaat aisi hain ke jis mein paai jaeyngi wo eman ki mithas pa lega awwal ye ke Allah aur uske rasool usey sabse zyada azeez hon. doosrey ye ke wo kisi shakhs se mohabbat sirf Allah hi ke liye karey teesrey ye ke usey kufr ki taraf lot kar jana itna na-gawar ho jaisey aag mein phenk diya jaanaa.''
6942,maine apne aapko is haal mein paya ke Islam laney ki wjah se (Makka muazzama mein) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey baandh diya tha aur ab jo kuchh tum ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath kya hai is par agar Uhud pahaad tukdey tukdey ho jaey to usey aisa hi hona chahiye
6943,ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apna haale-zaar bayan kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt Kaba ke saaye main apni chadar par baithey huey they. ham ne arz kya kyon nahi aap hamarey liye Allah Taala se madad maangtey aur Allah Taala se dua kartey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum se pahley bahut se nabiyon aur un par eman laney walon ka haal ye hua ke unmein se kisi aik ko pakad liya jata aur garhaa khod kar usmein unhein daal diya jata phir aaraa laya jata aur unke sar par rakh kar do tukdey kar diye jatey aur lohey ke kanghey unke gosht aur haddiyon mein dhansaa diye jatey lekin ye aazmaaishein bhi unhein apne Deen se nahi rok sakti thin. Allah ki qasam! is Islam ka kaam mukammal hoga aur aik sawar san'aa se hazare-Maut tak akelaa safar karega aur usey Allah ke siwa aur kisi ka khof nahi hoga aur bakriyon par siwa bhediye ke khof ke (aur kisi loot wghaira ka koi dar na hoga) lekin tum log jaldi kartey ho.
6944,ham masjid mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya ke yahudiyon ke paas chalo. ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey aur jab ham baitul-Midraas ke paas pahunchey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein awaz di aey qaume-yahood! Islam lao tum mehfooz ho jaogey. yahudiyon ne kaha : abul-Qaasim! aap ne pahuncha diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mera bhi yahi maqsad hai phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dobara yahi farmaya aur yahudiyon ne kaha ke abul-Qaasim aap ne pahuncha diya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri martaba yahi farmaya aur phir farmaya tumhen malum hona chahiye ke zameen Allah aur uske rasool ki hai aur main tumhen jilaa watan karta hun. to tum mein se jiske paas maal ho usey chahiye ke jilaa watan honey se pahley usey bech de warna jaan lo ke zameen Allah aur uske rasool ki hai.
6945,unke walid ne unki shadi kar di unki aik shadi us se pahley ho chuki thi (aur ab bewa thiin) is nikah ko unhon-ne na-pasand kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar (apni na-pasandidgi zahir kar di ( to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is nikah ko khatm kar diya.
6946,"maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya aurton se unke nikah ke silsile mein ijazat li jaeygi? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, haan. maine arz kya lekin kunwari ladki se ijazat li jaeygi to wo sharm ki wjah se chup saadh legii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski khamoshi hi ijazat hai."
6947,"aik Ansari sahabi ne kisi ghulam ko mudabbir banaya aur unke paas iske siwa aur koi maal nahi tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab uski itlaa mili to malum farmaya, usey mujh se kon khareedeyga chunanche Nuaim-bin-Nahaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne aath (8) so dirham mein khareed liya. bayan kya ke phir maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unhon-ne bayan kya ke wo aik qibtii ghulam tha aur pahley hi saal mar gaya."
6948,mujh se ata abul-Hasan-al-Suwaaii ne bayan kya aur mera yahi khayal hai ke unhon-ne ye hadis Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan ki. sura Mayeda ki aayat يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا يحل لكم أن ترثوا Nisa كرها bayaan kya ke jab koi shakhs (zamaana jahiliyat mein) mar jata to iske waaris uski aurat ke haqdaar bantey agar unmein se koi chahta to us se shadi kar leta aur chahta to shadi na karta is tarah marney waley ke waaris us aurat par aurat ke waarison se zyada haq rakhtey. is par ye aayat nazil hui (bewa aurat iddat guzarney ke baad Mukhtar hai wo jis se chahey shadi karey is par zabardastii karna hargiz jaaiz nahi hai).
6949,hukumat ke ghulaamon mein se aik ne hissey khums ki aik baandi se sohbat kar li aur uske sath zabardastii karke uski bikaarat tod di to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ghulam par had jari karaai aur usey Shahar badr bhi kar diya lekin baandi par had nahi jari ki. kyonke ghulam ne iske sath zabardastii ki thi. Zohri ne aisi kunwari baandi ke mutaalliq kaha jiske sath kisi aazad ne ham-bistarii kar li ho ke Hakim kunwari baandi mein uski wjah se us shakhs se itney daam bhar ley jitney bikaarat jatey rehney ki wjah se iske daam kam ho gaey hain aur usko kode bhi lagaey agar aazad mard Saiba londi se zina karey tab khareedey. imaamon ne ye hukm nahi diya hai ke usko kuchh maalii taawaan dena padega balke sirf had lagai jaeygi.
6950,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ne Saara (Alaihissalam) ko sath lekar hijrat ki to aik aisi basti mein pahunchey jis mein baadshaahon mein se aik badshah ya zaalimon mein se aik zaalim rehta tha us zaalim ne Ibrahim ke paas ye hukm bheja ke Saara (Alaihissalam) ko uske paas bhejein aap ne saara ko bhej diya wo zaalim unke paas aaya to wo (Saara (Alaihissalam) ( wuzu karke Namaz padh rahi thin unhon-ne dua ki ke aey Allaah! agar main tujh par aur terey rasool par eman rakhti hun to too mujh par kaafir ko na musallat kar phir aisa hua ke wo kambakht badshah achcha kharraatey leney aur gir kar paon hilaaney laga.
6951,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''musalmaan muslmaan ka bhai hai na is par zulm karey aur na usey ( kisi zaalim ke) sipurd karey aur jo shakhs apne kisi bhai ki zarurat poori karne mein laga hoga Allah Taala uski zarurat aur haajat poori karega.''
6952,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''apne bhai ki madad karo chahe wo zaalim ho ya mazloom.''eik sahabi ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! jab wo mazloom ho to main uski madad karunga lekin aap ka kya khayal hai jab wo zaalim hoga phir main uski madad kaisey karun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us waqt tum usey zulm se roknaa kyonke yahi uski madad hai.
